Arquitectura y estructura
Frontend
Stack: React 18, Vite, React Router, Tailwind.
Configs:
vite.config.mjs (ESM), proxy /api → http://localhost:3001, alias @ → /src.
postcss.config.mjs (ESM), tailwind.config.js.
Rutas/páginas (base): Home, ImportExcel, DataTable, Register, Login, AdminDashboard.
Auth: JWT en localStorage, setAuthToken en api.js.
Estilos: src/index.css o src/styles/globals.css con @tailwind base/components/utilities.
Backend
Stack: Node 18+ ESM ("type":"module"), Express, Mongoose, Multer, XLSX, dotenv, CORS.
